\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f2\lang7177\f3\f2\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851 [36]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af2\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f2\fs24\lang7177\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177\i0\b0 We conclude that parties in our proceedings are entitled to litigation privilege and that no exception exists to deny such a privilege to the Commission.}
