\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\lang7177\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851 [39]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang7177\loch\f3\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 That in the process an ancillary outcome, the award of indemnity is afforded, does not detract from fact that the Commission\'92s central object is to use the information to conduct litigation in the Tribunal against such members of the alleged cartel as cont
est proceedings. Thus the inescapable conclusion is that inherent in this process is the contemplation of litigation. }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\lang7177\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851 [40]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang7177\loch\f3\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 There is thus no basis for refusing to recognise litigation privilege because the statements in question were generated through the CLP process.}
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f3\fs22\lang7177\f3\fs22\f3\fs22\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851 [41]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af3\afs22\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f3\fs22\lang7177\loch\f3\fs22\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f3\fs22\lang7177\i0\b0\rtlch\ltrch\hich\f2\loch\f2 In summary then we find that the Commission is entitled to claim litigation privilege in our proceedings and that the statements made in this matter in the course of the CLP fall within that privilege. }
\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\f2\lang7177\f3\f2\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851 [42]\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s1\sl360\slmult1\qj\tx851{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls1\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\sa200\rtlch\af2\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f2\fs24\lang7177\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f2\fs24\lang7177\i0\b0 We therefore make no order for further and better discovery and the application is dismissed. }
